    "PracticalityTwo relevant studies aim to improve the practicality of code generators.",
    "Dong et al. [103] introduced a structure-aware neural architecture for code generation that exhibits adaptability to diverse domains and representations.",
    "Shen et al. [104] proposed a task augmentation technique that integrates domain knowledge into code generation models, making their model the first domain-specific code generation system adopted in industrial development environments.",
